BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260310T215538Z
UID:31f1b30e5f1c53b3a22007f8ce55eec09a33d20b@myvmk
SUMMARY:Double Credits
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260307T050000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260308T060000
DESCRIPTION:Host: MyVMK Staff\nFor 24 hours\, you will earn DOUBLE the cred
 its by playing MyVMK Mini Games! With swashbuckling battles at sea\, haun
 ting ghost hunts\, animal photo expeditions\, and exciting pyrotechnic pe
 rformances\, there are so many ways to play and earn! See you in the lobb
 ies!
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260310T215538Z
UID:fc47cb42ed4d1713d1337cfbe76ad4b85c2bedfa@myvmk
SUMMARY:Help Grow The Plants
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260307T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260307T180000
DESCRIPTION:Host: HOST_Morph\nWill your team grow plants fastest?\n\nNote
 :  This event has green plants on top of red sand carpets. For those that
  are color blind\, you may not be able differentiate between the two colo
 rs. 
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260310T215538Z
UID:3c56c1973ee8e2206ae854caa7905fcf7321fd5f@myvmk
SUMMARY:Green as a 4 Leaf Clover!
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260311T000000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260311T010000
DESCRIPTION:Host: Host_JudyHopps\nLooking for the green of a 4 leaf clover.
  First team to both spin green wins! Wait for me to tell you when to spin
 ! If you need a number generator please request one. In that case you wil
 l need to spin a 4 instead of green.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260310T215538Z
UID:7e789a8bde78ff44cb14696f3013262f3d805a8b@myvmk
SUMMARY:Fairy Face-off
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260312T020000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260312T030000
DESCRIPTION:Host: HOST_LadyTremaine\nWelcome to Princess Aurora's Castle!\
 n\n- 2 Teams of 2 enter the castle and sit on either the pink or green s
 ide.\n\n- When I say "Go" you will spin your generator until you land o
 n Maleficent\n\n- After Rolling Maleficent on your gen\, click your rid
 e start and race to destroy all the spinning wheels (double click gems)\
 n(you can go through as many times as it takes to light up all your gems)
 \n\n- Once you light up all your gems sit back in your seat and double 
 click the hat above your gen to light it!\n\n- First team to light up a
 ll their gems and hats win!
END:VEVENT
